### 🎛️ Optical Path & Filters

{% set dto = lightpath_dto %}
{% if dto and dto.stages %}

{# 1. Render Filter Cubes as nested bullets #}
{% if dto.stages.cube %}
#### 🧊 Filter Cubes (Linked Mechanisms)
{% for mech in dto.stages.cube %}
**{{ mech.name }}**
{% for pos in mech.positions %}
* **Slot {{ pos.slot }}: {{ pos.label }}** {% if pos.details %}— *{{ pos.details }}*{% endif %}
  {% if pos.linked_components.excitation_filter.type != "empty" or pos.linked_components.dichroic.type != "empty" or pos.linked_components.emission_filter.type != "empty" %}
    * **Excitation:** `{{ pos.linked_components.excitation_filter.label | default('-') }}`
    * **Dichroic:** `{{ pos.linked_components.dichroic.label | default('-') }}`
    * **Emission:** `{{ pos.linked_components.emission_filter.label | default('-') }}`
  {% else %}
    * *Pass-through (Empty)*
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{# 2. Render Independent Stages as clean lists #}
{% for stage_key in ['excitation', 'dichroic', 'emission'] %}
{% set mechanisms = dto.stages[stage_key] %}
{% if mechanisms %}
#### ⭕ {{ stage_key | title }} Stage
{% for mech in mechanisms %}
**{{ mech.name }}**
{% for pos in mech.positions %}
* **Slot {{ pos.slot }}:** `{{ pos.label }}` {% if pos.details %}— *{{ pos.details }}*{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% endif %}

{# 3. Render Splitters as routing lists #}
{% if dto and dto.splitters %}
#### 🔀 Splitters & Light Routing
{% for splitter in dto.splitters %}
**{{ splitter.name }}**
* **Dichroic:** `{{ splitter.dichroic.positions[1].label | default('None') }}` {% if splitter.dichroic.positions[1].details %}(*{{ splitter.dichroic.positions[1].details }}*){% endif %}
* **Path 1 (Transmitted):** `{{ splitter.path1.positions[1].label | default('None') }}` {% if splitter.path1.positions[1].details %}(*{{ splitter.path1.positions[1].details }}*){% endif %}
* **Path 2 (Reflected):** `{{ splitter.path2.positions[1].label | default('None') }}` {% if splitter.path2.positions[1].details %}(*{{ splitter.path2.positions[1].details }}*){% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}


